		<item>
			<title>Результаты Финалов Шести</title>
			<link>https://noginsk-volley.ru/index.php/new/2-rezultaty-finalov-shesti.html</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">https://noginsk-volley.ru/index.php/new/2-rezultaty-finalov-shesti.html</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://noginsk-volley.ru/images/slider/6.jpg" /></p><h2 style="margin: 1em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; text-align: center; color: #525252 !important;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Состоялись мужские и женские Финалы Шести НЛВЛ</span></strong></h2>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><strong>По результатам сформировались полуфиналисты:</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong>Мужчины </strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Первая пара полуфиналистов "Павловский-Посад" <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Павловский-Посад - "Гвозди" Электросталь </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em>Начало игры 22 апреля в 10.00</em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Вторая пара полуфиналистов "Богородск" Ногинск - "Электроугли" </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Электроугли </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em style="font-size: 12.96px;">Начало игры 22 апреля в 12.00</em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em style="font-size: 12.96px;"> </em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong>Женщины </strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Первая пара полуфиналистов "Жемчужина" Пушкино - "Интрига" </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Павловский-Посад</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"> </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em style="font-size: 12.96px;">Начало игры 22 апреля в 15.00</em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Вторая пара полуфиналистов "Литвиново" </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Литвиново - "Агат" Ногинск</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em style="font-size: 12.96px;">Начало игры 22 апреля в 17.00</em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em style="font-size: 12.96px;"> </em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em style="font-size: 12.96px;">Игры будут проходить </em><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-family: tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif, 'Lucida Sans'; text-align: right;">г.Ногинск </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: right; font-family: tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif, 'Lucida Sans'; line-height: 16.5px;">ДДЮТ ул. III </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: right; font-family: tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif, 'Lucida Sans'; line-height: 16.5px;">Интернационала</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: right; font-family: tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif, 'Lucida Sans'; line-height: 16.5px;">, д. 117</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em style="font-size: 12.96px;"> </em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em style="font-size: 12.96px;">Результаты игр Финалов шести:</em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em style="font-size: 12.96px;">Мужчины вторая подгруппа:  </em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">"Богородск" Ногинск - </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">"Гвозди" Электросталь 3-1</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">"Гвозди" Электросталь - "Семь ветров" </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Павловский-Посад 3-1</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"> </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">"Богородск" Ногинск - </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">"Семь ветров" </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Павловский-Посад 3-0</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"> </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><em style="font-size: 12.96px;">Мужчины первая подгруппа:</em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">"Электросталь" </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Электросталь - "</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Павловский-Посад"</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"> </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Павловский-Посад 1-3</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #fbfcfc; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">"Электросталь" </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Электросталь - </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">"Электроугли" </span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12.96px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Электроугли 1-3</span></p>]]></description>
